  * Initial release of unified AGI Operating System
  * Complete three-layer architecture integration
  * Layer 1: Cognumach enhanced microkernel
  * Layer 2: HurdCog cognitive operating system
  * Layer 3: OpenCog Collection AGI framework
  * Cognitive synergy across all system layers
  * Distributed hypergraph processing
  * Real-time cognitive monitoring and dashboard
  * Self-optimization and learning capabilities
  * Probabilistic reasoning and attention allocation
  * Production-ready Debian packaging
  * GNU Guix reproducible build support
  * Complete development environment
  * World's first AGI-native operating system

